Macquarie Investment Management Limited: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 26, 2017 7:56 AM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Macquarie Investment Management Limited



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Macquarie Investment Management Limited operates as an investment arm of Macquarie Bank Limited. The firm primarily provides its services to institutional and retails clients. It manages mutual funds for its clients. The firm invests in the public equity and fixed income markets of Australia. It also seek to make private equity investments through its funds Macquarie Alternative Investment Trust. Macquarie Investment Management was founded in November 1984 and is based in New South Wales, Australia.


20 Bond StreetLevel 27Sydney, NSW 2000AustraliaFounded in 1984



Phone: 61 2 8232 3333

Fax: 61 2 8232 4730

www.macquarie.com.au/mgl/au/mfg/mim







